<br>
He may be worth 200 million, but he will either be funded by outsiders or he will run out of cash real fast.  Either way it doesn't matter because it is obvious he has lots of people that are willing to die for free.<br>
<br>
Vietnam is a prime example (don't get into whether or not we should have been there, or whether or not we commited enough effort)... enemies knew the land, they dug tunnels and hid.  We need to dump in the "gas," light it and smoke them out is all (yes, I know, over simplification more analogy than realism).<br>
<br>
Either way.. if you talk about the rights of innocent Americans and you support in ANY way the persecution, verbal or otherwise, of american citizens of arab origin (sorry if this is not pc term) then you are a HYPOCRITE and need to be persecuted to the fullest extent of the law.  You are NOT a patriot, and I venture to say that the dead in NY and DC would be ASHAMED of you.  <br>
<br>
Not only are you not helping, but you are as bad as the terrorists.  You are trying to make a point by hurting innocents.  You claim to be protecting Americans, or the American ideal and yet you forget one of our major protections... and you declare guilt before guilt is proven.  In America, it doesn't matter if you laugh over the dead, if you spit on the flag, you are scum - worthless flesh - but you are still innocent of a crime until the court declares you guilty, and the COURT will decide your sentence.  If you dole out your own version of your own justice you are nothing but a rogue, something about as unamerican as you can get.<br>
<br>
